<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>한수협 후원 제안서 - Premium Edition (AI Powered)</title>
    <!-- 고급스러운 폰트 (Pretendard & Montserrat) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Color Palette */
            --primary: #0A2463;       /* Deep Navy */
            --secondary: #1E3A8A;     /* Ocean Blue */
            --accent: #00D2D3;        /* Vibrant Cyan */
            --accent-light: #E0FBFC;  /* Light Cyan */
            --text-dark: #1E293B;     /* Slate 800 */
            --text-gray: #64748B;     /* Slate 500 */
            --bg-main: #F4F7F9;       /* Light Gray Blue */
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --danger: #EF4444;        /* Red for problems */
            --ai-glow: #8B5CF6;       /* Purple for AI Magic */
            
            /* Gradients */
            --grad-ocean: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            --grad-accent: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D2D3 0%, #03A9F4 100%);
            --grad-ai: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6 0%, #D946EF 100%);
            
            /* Shadows & Radius */
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 25px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 40px -5px rgba(10, 36, 99, 0.15);
            --radius-lg: 24px;
            --radius-md: 16px;
        }

        /* CORE DESIGN PRINCIPLES */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { 
            background-color: #E2E8F0; 
            padding: 40px 0; 
            display: grid; 
            gap: 40px; 
            place-items: center; 
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; 
            color: var(--text-dark);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .slide-container { 
            width: 1280px; 
            height: 720px; 
            background-color: var(--white); 
            position: relative; 
            overflow: hidden; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            padding: 70px 80px; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); 
            border-radius: 12px; 
        }

        /* Abstract Background Elements */
        .decor-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(80px);
            z-index: 0;
            opacity: 0.4;
        }
        .decor-1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: var(--accent); top: -100px; right: -100px; }
        .decor-2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: var(--secondary); bottom: -50px; left: -50px; }

        /* TYPOGRAPHY */
        h1, h2, h3, h4 { color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        p, li { color: var(--text-gray); line-height: 1.6; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        
        .slide-title { 
            font-size: 40px; 
            margin-bottom: 50px; 
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .slide-title::before {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 6px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--grad-accent);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        
        .slide-title span {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .content-area { flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; width: 100%; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

        /* GRADIENT TEXT */
        .text-gradient {
            background: var(--grad-accent);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        /* IMAGE PLACEHOLDER */
        .image-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .image-placeholder::after {
            content: '\f03e';
            font-family: 'Font Awesome 6 Free';
            font-weight: 900;
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 120px;
            opacity: 0.05;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* LAYOUTS */
        .cover-slide { padding: 0; background: var(--grad-ocean); color: var(--white); justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; }
        .cover-slide::before {
            content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none"><polygon fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)" points="0,100 100,0 100,100"/></svg>');
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .cover-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        .cover-badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 50px; font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); color: var(--accent); }
        .cover-title { font-size: 68px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 25px; color: var(--white); }
        .cover-subtitle { font-size: 26px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .cover-logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; opacity: 0.9; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }

        .transition-slide { background: var(--bg-main); text-align: center; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .transition-slide h2 { font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .transition-slide p { font-size: 28px; color: var(--text-gray); }
        .transition-icon { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 40px; color: var(--accent); animation: bounce 2s infinite; }

        @keyframes bounce { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(15px); } }

        .two-column { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center; }
        .image-wrapper { width: 100%; height: 420px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }

        .card-grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 30px; }
        .card { 
            background: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 40px; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px; background: var(--grad-accent); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease; }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
        .card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
        
        .card-icon { width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--primary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .card h3 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: var(--primary); }
        .card p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; }

        .problem-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
        .problem-list li { background: #FEF2F2; border-left: 4px solid var(--danger); padding: 20px 25px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 18px; color: #7F1D1D; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; font-weight: 500; }
        .problem-list li i { color: var(--danger); font-size: 24px; }

        .target-badges { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .target-badge { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; background: var(--white); padding: 25px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .target-badge-icon { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--primary); color: white; border-radius: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; }
        .target-badge-text h4 { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: var(--primary); }
        .target-badge-text p { font-size: 16px; margin: 0; }

        .stats-container { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .stat-box { flex: 1; background: var(--white); padding: 40px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .stat-number { font-family: 'Montserrat'; font-size: 72px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; background: var(--grad-ocean); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .stat-label { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-gray); }
        
        .esg-banner { background: var(--primary); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 40px; text-align: center; color: white; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .esg-banner h3 { color: white; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .esg-banner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 20px; margin: 0; }

        .slide-container.bleed-layout { padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        .bleed-content { padding: 80px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
        .bleed-image { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
        
        .check-list { list-style: none; margin-top: 30px; }
        .check-list li { font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px; }
        .check-list li i { color: var(--accent); font-size: 24px; margin-top: 3px; }

        .premium-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .premium-table th { background: var(--bg-main); color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; padding: 20px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1; }
        .premium-table td { padding: 25px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; background: var(--white); font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-dark); }
        .premium-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
        .premium-table td strong { color: var(--primary); font-size: 18px; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }

        .closing-slide { text-align: center; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: var(--white); padding: 40px; }
        .closing-title { font-size: 56px; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .contact-chips { display: flex; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 30px; }
        .contact-chip { background: var(--bg-main); padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 50px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--primary); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
        .contact-chip i { color: var(--accent); font-size: 22px; }

        /* =========================================================
           ✨ GEMINI AI FEATURES CSS
           ========================================================= */
        .ai-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff, #f8f9fa);
            border: 2px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .ai-panel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px;
            background: var(--grad-ai);
        }
        .ai-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .ai-header h4 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #5B21B6;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .ai-input-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .ai-input {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #D1D5DB;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: inherit;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }
        .ai-input:focus { border-color: var(--ai-glow); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); }
        .ai-btn {
            background: var(--grad-ai);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .ai-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3); }
        .ai-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
        
        .ai-result-box {
            background: #F8FAFC;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            min-height: 80px;
            max-height: 250px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: none; /* hidden by default */
        }
        .ai-result-box.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease; }
        .ai-result-box strong { color: #5B21B6; }
        .ai-result-box ul { padding-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px; }
        .ai-result-box li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

        /* Loader */
        .loader {
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-top: 3px solid white;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            display: none;
        }
        .loading .loader { display: block; }
        .loading .btn-text { display: none; }

        @keyframes spin { 0% { transform: rotate(0deg); } 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Slide 1: Cover -->
    <div class="slide-container cover-slide">
        <div class="cover-content">
            <div class="cover-badge">SPONSORSHIP PROPOSAL</div>
            <h1 class="cover-title">지속 가능한 바다,<br>풍요로운 내일을 위한 동행</h1>
            <p class="cover-subtitle">사단법인 한국비어업인수산자원보호협회 공식 후원 제안서</p>
            <div class="cover-logo">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-water" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 28px;"></i>
                KOREA NON-FISHERMEN MARINE RESOURCES PROTECTION ASSOC.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 2: Problem -->
    <div class="slide-container">
        <div class="decor-circle decor-1"></div>
        <div class="slide-title">
            <div>
                <span>The Challenge</span>
                우리 바다가 직면한 새로운 과제
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-area">
            <div class="two-column">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-dark);">
                        급증하는 해양 레저 인구,<br><span style="color: var(--danger);">심화되는 갈등과 위협</span>
                    </h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                        최근 해루질, 프리다이빙, 낚시 등 비어업인의 해양 활동이 폭발적으로 증가하며 <b>어촌계와의 마찰 및 수산자원 고갈 우려</b>가 심각한 사회적 문제로 대두되고 있습니다.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="problem-list">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> 무분별한 불법 포획 및 어구 훼손으로 인한 경제적 손실</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-life-ring"></i> 해양 안전 수칙 미준수로 인한 지속적인 인명 사고 발생</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-slash"></i> 생존권이 걸린 지역 어민과 방문객 간의 감정적 대립 심화</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <div class="image-placeholder">
                        <span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 3: Mission -->
    <div class="slide-container">
        <div class="slide-title">
            <div>
                <span>Who We Are</span>
                우리는 상생의 다리를 놓습니다
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-area">
            <div class="card-grid-3">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-anchor"></i></div>
                    <h3>설립 목적</h3>
                    <p>무조건적인 금지가 아닌, 비어업인의 건전한 수산자원 포획 문화를 정착시키고 어민과의 실질적인 상생 협력 모델을 구축합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
                    <h3>공식 미션</h3>
                    <p>해양수산부 허가 비영리 사단법인으로서 수산자원 보호 관련 법령 준수를 홍보하고, 체계적인 해양 활동 안전 교육을 시행합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i></div>
                    <h3>미래 비전</h3>
                    <p>수산자원의 철저한 보호와 레저로서의 올바른 이용이 조화를 이루는 '지속 가능한 대한민국 바다'를 여러분과 함께 실현합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 4: Transition -->
    <div class="slide-container transition-slide">
        <h2>WHY PARTNER WITH US?</h2>
        <p>왜 한수협과 함께 동행해야 할까요?</p>
        <div class="transition-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down"></i></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 5: Target -->
    <div class="slide-container">
        <div class="decor-circle decor-2"></div>
        <div class="slide-title">
            <div>
                <span>Audience</span>
                확실하고 집중된 고관여 타겟
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-area">
            <div class="two-column">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                    <div class="image-placeholder">
                        <span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 15px;">레저 시장의 '헤비 유저'를 만나다</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px;">협회 회원들은 단순 관광객이 아닙니다. 관련 장비에 대한 투자를 아끼지 않으며, 정기적이고 적극적으로 활동하는 귀사의 진성 고객층입니다.</p>
                    
                    <div class="target-badges">
                        <div class="target-badge">
                            <div class="target-badge-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-fish-fins"></i></div>
                            <div class="target-badge-text">
                                <h4>해루질 & 낚시 타겟</h4>
                                <p>수중 랜턴, 가슴 장화, 전문 낚시 장비 고관여층</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="target-badge">
                            <div class="target-badge-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-campground"></i></div>
                            <div class="target-badge-text">
                                <h4>아웃도어 & 캠핑 타겟</h4>
                                <p>해안 노지 캠핑 장비, 프리미엄 아웃도어 의류 수요층</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Slide 6: Network & ESG -->
    <div class="slide-container">
        <div class="slide-title">
            <div>
                <span>Impact</span>
                강력한 네트워크와 ESG 가치 실현
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-area">
            <div class="stats-container">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <div class="stat-number">1,891</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">협회 정회원 (명)</div>
